  <scopecontent id="aspace_17d8e222c0967e8da4daadf4b6e93322">
    <head>Scope and Contents</head>
<p>The collection documents the Anson G. Phelps lectures though promotional materials such as posters, leaflets and brochures, as well as printed manuscripts that contain the lectures given or manuscripts that the lectures were based on.</p>  </scopecontent>
